org.svvrl.goal.core.comp.slice

Class SliceVWHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.svvrl.goal.core.comp.slice.SliceHelper<SliceVW>
      • org.svvrl.goal.core.comp.slice.SliceVWHelper

  • public class SliceVWHelper
extends SliceHelper<SliceVW>
    A SliceVWHelper is a helper class for the preliminary version of the slice-based construction [Moshe Y. Vardi and Thomas Wilke. Automata: from logics to algorithms. In Logic and Automata: History and Perspective, volume 2 of Texts in Logic and Games, pages 629-736. Amsterdam University Press, 2007]. The options SliceVWOptions.isEnhancedGuessing() and SliceVWOptions.isMergeAdjacent() are taken care in this class.
    Author:
    Ming-Hsien Tsai
